data.description: Hidden gem in Southfield with almost a quarter acre to enjoy nestled on the last lot on a quiet, secluded dead end street. This is a great starter home or investment property with four bedrooms and one bath. Easily convert the two bedrooms upstairs into one huge Master! Huge fenced in back yard, perfect for children, pets or RV. Concrete shed. New roof 2017, newer water tank 2013. All the window a/c units included in sale. One year home warranty through America's Preferred Home Warranty also included in sale. Value in both home and land.
